nodes.text: The Kashyyyk seven layer cake was a spherical dessert which consisted of seven distinct layers and an outer coating of syrup and chocolate. The cake did not originated in Kashyyyk but was name as such due to the ingredients originating from the planet.

The cake was made with Wyyyschokk eggs, which had to first be boiled slowly to rid them of toxins. Traditionally, the cake was baked. However, according to Sean, the baking process destroyed the best flavors of the ingredients native to Kashyyyk, so his recipe omitted that step. Jedi Padawan Sean once made a special Kashyyyk cake which gave Jamie Brasen an allergic reaction.
